    "patch_code": "private static boolean contains(List<String> list, Method method){\n     final int lastIndexOfSlash = method.getName().lastIndexOf('/');\n    final String simpleName = lastIndexOfSlash == -1 ? method.getName() :\n           method.getName().substring(lastIndexOfSlash + 1);\n    return list.contains(simpleName);\n}",
